{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_vrtx_014mfhkmgjqnrSmF9bom7pBg","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# csv2json\n2\t\n3\tA lightweight CLI tool for converting CSV files to JSON format.\n4\t\n5\t## Installation\n6\t\n7\t```bash\n8\tpip install csv2json\n9\t```\n10\t\n11\tOr install from source:\n12\t\n13\t```bash\n14\tpip install -e .\n15\t```\n16\t\n17\t## Usage\n18\t\n19\tConvert a CSV file to JSON:\n20\t\n21\t```bash\n22\tcsv2json convert input.csv output.json\n23\t```\n24\t\n25\tSpecify custom indentation:\n26\t\n27\t```bash\n28\tcsv2json convert input.csv output.json --indent 4\n29\t```\n30\t\n31\t## Features\n32\t\n33\t- Reads CSV files using pandas for robust parsing\n34\t- Outputs well-formatted JSON with configurable indentation\n35\t- Handles common CSV edge cases (quoted fields, varied delimiters)\n36\t\n37\t## Development\n38\t\n39\tInstall dev dependencies:\n40\t\n41\t```bash\n42\tpip install -e \".[dev]\"\n43\t```\n44\t\n45\tRun tests:\n46\t\n47\t```bash\n48\tpytest\n49\t```\n50\t\n51\tLint:\n52\t\n53\t```bash\n54\truff check src/ tests/\n55\t```\n56\t\n57\t## Built With\n58\t\n59\t- [Click](https://click.palletsprojects.com/) -- CLI framework\n60\t- [pandas](https://pandas.pydata.org/) -- CSV parsing\n61\t\n62\t## License\n63\t\n64\tMIT\n65\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3b78be28-0a3d-483f-ba08-8a03331f54f3","uuid":"1e2f8849-2e68-4269-a0c5-cf0687388875","timestamp":"2026-06-23T14:45:44.625Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/private/var/folders/38/_z2xr8rn0m33jpdp5jkbmd500000gn/T/agent-eval/2026-06-23-opus/cases/case-001-simple-python-cli/README.md","content":"# csv2json\n\nA lightweight CLI tool for converting CSV files to JSON format.\n\n## Installation\n\n```bash\npip install csv2json\n```\n\nOr install from source:\n\n```bash\npip install -e .\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nConvert a CSV file to JSON:\n\n```bash\ncsv2json convert input.csv output.json\n```\n\nSpecify custom indentation:\n\n```bash\ncsv2json convert input.csv output.json --indent 4\n```\n\n## Features\n\n- Reads CSV files using pandas for robust parsing\n- Outputs well-formatted JSON with configurable indentation\n- Handles common CSV edge cases (quoted fields, varied delimiters)\n\n## Development\n\nInstall dev dependencies:\n\n```bash\npip install -e \".[dev]\"\n```\n\nRun tests:\n\n```bash\npytest\n```\n\nLint:\n\n```bash\nruff check src/ tests/\n```\n\n## Built With\n\n- [Click](https://click.palletsprojects.com/) -- CLI framework\n- [pandas](https://pandas.pydata.org/) -- CSV parsing\n\n## License\n\nMIT\n","numLines":65,"startLine":1,"totalLines":65}}}
